{"tid":1492846,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］有網上聯署BNO平權，點解冇去領事館請願？","createTime":"2019-08-21T04:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:35:50.000Z","uid":95469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85429b354a107b8385df99674a745028da533861","tid":1492846,"uid":95469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"有BNO既人(包括未續）一齊去英國駐港總領事館外請願有冇得諗？請願係無人數門檻，而且比聯署更直接有效。例如係大使館門外高舉護照唱God Save the Queen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，遞交請願信等。有幾多人會出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233d7847b62a0fbfa75d9c333e9eda02464bf77a","tid":1492846,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"算數啦，連聯署都無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defb29ea588986a14dfa07944d6a27e3e21fcc09","tid":1492846,"uid":171509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"九月一會去英領集會<br />\n詳見其他連登post"},{"pid":"5114041ee89efed3554f8440572a488c739acbd7","tid":1492846,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33e9f4beb2f146320cb8768dce938576f1b5fcc7","tid":1492846,"uid":95469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"此post已完！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f15f8bbcae7ffe3c1e4b11642a508bb989b6f64","tid":1492846,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYgmjQj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYgmjQj.jpg&h=3d091ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊得話無"},{"pid":"7a1de4ba580fa04457c2887a35c3933b9dedf21e","tid":1492846,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"叫埋上一代人簽，佢地唔識上連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41FSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=3afded49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"c245d873ab7a41bf3bc28a022ea5c03a3d29c277","tid":1492846,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"BNO平權文宣方向<br />\n不過, 從7月開始, 英國輿論 &ndash; 從每日快報, 衛報, 觀察者, 甚至太陽報紛紛鼓吹<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>英國政府應給予BNO持有者BC身份</ins></strong></span>. 值得一提的是英國智庫Adam Smith Institute在8月15日出了一份名為Doing Our Duty的研究報告, 建議<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國政府應將BNO權利擴大至與BC同等</span></ins></strong>, 因為若BNO人成為BC, 這&rdquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>將會促使中國和平地行事</ins></strong></span>&rdquo; (p. 6), 香港人可以&rdquo;在自由的環境下生活, 而中國則失去一整代人,<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"> 英國會得到道德和物質上的勝利</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 7). 不只如此, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人&rdquo;人均收入高, 高學歷及具備專業技能, 對英國經濟會有實質益處</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 8). 最後, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國幫BNO升級可顯示英國&rdquo;並未忘記其角色和放棄原則&rdquo;</span></ins></strong> (p. 9). 這份報告暗示: a. BNO是&rdquo;和平時代&rdquo;的產物. 只要中英間利益衝突, BNO會是英國的招數: 中國領土內突然出現大批BC會<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">使英國有理由介入香港事務</span></ins></strong>, 這也是為什麼當初英國不給港人BC身份, 卻要弄出BNO, 而中國則要強加中國籍給香港人的根本原因 (英國不要收留港人; 中國收港人, 但條件是&rdquo;管得了&rdquo;的港人. 反正要抓人只要說句他是&rdquo;中國人&rdquo;就行) (結論1和3); b. 英國對香港的&rdquo;道義和責任&rdquo;乃建基在利益上, 尤其<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">正值英國脫歐, 香港將可成為英國經濟的救火員</span></ins></strong> (結論2)."}]}